Convention sharing with skill-refactor
---------------------------------------

This skill bundles **functional copies** of 3 shared convention
files in `references/`:

- `golden-anchor-protocol.md`
- `test-prompts-schema.md`
- `constitution-schema.md`

Same-PR drift rule (per the SSOT-and-functional-copy precedent set
in PR #159):

- The canonical SoT for these conventions lives in
  `skill-dev-toolkit:skill-refactor/references/`
- Edits to a convention land in skill-refactor first, then mirror
  here in the **same PR**
- Bundled copies in this skill carry header blockquotes pointing
  back to the canonical location for clarity

This arrangement preserves runtime self-containment (each skill
runs with `dev-workflow` alone, no cross-plugin or cross-skill
runtime dependency) while keeping evolution coherent.
